- [x] Step 1: Fetch PR metadata + diff + file stats via Octokit
- [x] Step 2: Retrieve RAG context from Pinecone
- [x] Step 3: Generate review via Gemini 2.5 Flash
- [x] Step 4: Post review comment on GitHub PR
- [x] Step 5: Save Review + ReviewDetail + FileChange records to DB
- [x] Concurrency limit: 5 simultaneous reviews
- [x] FREE tier review quota: 5 per repo

