- [x] [module/ai/lib/rag.ts](file:///c:/Users/prana/OneDrive/Desktop/codelensai/module/ai/lib/rag.ts) — embed + index + retrieve
- [x] Pinecone `codelens` index (3072 dims, Google embeddings)
- [x] Context injected into review prompt

