**Data flow:**

```
Page loads → getCollaborators(repoId)
  ↓
GitHub API (live list) + DB query (FileChange, ReviewDetail for activity stats)
  ↓
Merge: GitHub collaborator objects + local activity data
  ↓
Render cards with both permission info AND activity stats
```

