## 🔴 PHASE 7 — Incremental Repository Indexing

> 📄 Full spec: [diff/06-feature-incremental-indexing.md](file:///c:/Users/prana/OneDrive/Desktop/codelensai/diff/06-feature-incremental-indexing.md)

**Goal:** Replace costly full-repo indexing with smart delta indexing. Fix #1 scalability risk.

### Key Changes

- [ ] Add `IndexingState` model to schema (lastCommitSHA, status, indexedFiles count)
- [ ] Rewrite [inngest/functions/index.ts](file:///c:/Users/prana/OneDrive/Desktop/codelensai/inngest/functions/index.ts) to use Git Trees API (1 call vs 120+)
- [ ] `module/ai/lib/file-prioritizer.ts` — prioritize `src/`, `.ts/.tsx` files
- [ ] Create `inngest/functions/incremental-index.ts` — triggered per PR
- [ ] Create `inngest/functions/sync-index.ts` — daily cron at 3 AM
- [ ] UI: show indexing status badge per repo in Settings
- [ ] "Re-index" button per repo (rate limited: 1/hour)

